          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-copy-22-1697021659229-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add 80ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[160ml] </span><strong>milk</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>cider vinegar </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> free range</strong> <strong>chicken thighs </strong>to the <strong>marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up, then set aside until later</p><p>Tip: This will help to tenderise your chicken!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
