    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard all the excess marinade from the chicken</p><p>Add the <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> cornflour </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and a generous grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up until the chicken is fully coated</p>",
      "order": 6,
