    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, spread a little bit of the <strong>ranch-style dip </strong>on the base of the <strong>warmed brioche halves</strong>, top with a handful of the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong> and the <strong>fried free range chicken</strong>, then<strong> </strong>drizzle the <strong>buffalo sauce</strong> over the top</p><p>Top with the <strong>warmed brioche bun lids</strong> and serve the <strong>fries </strong>with the <strong>remaining quick-pickled cucumber </strong>and <strong>ranch-style dip</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
